<ab>Frawn Elisabeth, <expan>marggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>burggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Erhart
                            <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Vollands, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> knechte und
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> des <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Newstett<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> davon zu reden. Et
                            <expan>roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
                        credencie. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonii.</ab>
